---
title: Cheesy Stuffed Chicken and Sweet Potato Mash with Crunchy Spring Salad
description: Stuffing chicken breast with anything can add a je-ne-sais-quoi to meals on any night of the week. This cheesy chive  stuffed chicken is just that! Paired with a bright salad and creamy sweet potato mash, it's a winner!
